title: Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 X86 24in1 Pre-Activated en-US Sept 2013
description:
Win7.x86.24in1.en-US.Sept2013

[ RELEASE INFO ]

  Hotfixes 2013-09-10 included

  File:		Win7.x86.24in1.en-US.Sept2013.iso
  Source:	X17-59463 & Enterprise: Original DVD (677651)
	
  Size: 	3,20GB
  Format: 	Bootable ISO (DVD 4,7GB or USB)
   
  CRC32: 	a6d17ba8
  MD5:		dadeb7d11a0eeb6efc41489143753063
  SHA-1: 	e919c9a30c6e32bf080782fd424a5ef20fc9be16
   
[ CONTENTS ]

  Setupcomplete / Post-install:
  * KB890930
  * Defender updates 
  * .NET Framework 4.5.1 RC (only on marked editions)
  * Internet Explorer 10 

  Limited to Pre-Activated:
  * Windows Loader 2.2.1 by Daz (Enterprise KMS)

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

  * Windows 7 Starter        | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Home Basic     | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Home Premium   | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Professional   | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Ultimate       | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Enterprise     | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1


[ COMMENTS ]

  Setup information:
  * There are 4 different types of installation to choose from for each edition;

    1. Standard install
    2. Standard install with Activation
    3. Standard install with .NET 4.5.1 
    4. Standard install with .NET 4.5.1 and Activation
  
  * Indexes shown with Pre-Activated in the description field will be activated.
 <a href=" http://i.imgur.com/mMnDOG8.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://i.imgur.com/mMnDOG8.png</a>

  * Indexes with .NET 4.5.1 in the name will install .NET 4.5.1 RC
